463
00:56:02,271 --> 00:56:07,063
The Bishops will pass no measure
which severs us from Rome.

464
00:56:10,029 --> 00:56:14,073
Your Majesty would improve
all these matters

465
00:56:14,158 --> 00:56:16,446
if you would agree to marry.

466
00:56:16,535 --> 00:56:18,574
Aye. Marry, Madam.

467
00:56:19,413 --> 00:56:23,540
Aye. But marry who, Your Grace ?

468
00:56:24,501 --> 00:56:27,371
Will you give me some suggestion ?

469
00:56:28,713 --> 00:56:32,840
For some say France,
and others Spain, and

470
00:56:32,967 --> 00:56:36,382
and some cannot abide foreigners at all.

471
00:56:36,471 --> 00:56:41,595
So I'm not sure how best to please you
unless I married one of each.

472
00:56:46,564 --> 00:56:50,643
Now Your Majesty does make fun
of the sanctity of marriage.

473
00:56:50,734 --> 00:56:55,442
