on that, my Lord,

474
00:56:55,530 --> 00:56:59,657
since you yourself
have been twice divorced.

475
00:56:59,743 --> 00:57:02,779
And are now upon your third wife !

476
00:57:09,168 --> 00:57:13,295
Each of you must vote
according to your conscience.

477
00:57:15,216 --> 00:57:17,255
But remember this.

478
00:57:18,427 --> 00:57:20,668
In your hands,

479
00:57:21,555 --> 00:57:23,796
upon this moment,

480
00:57:24,766 --> 00:57:28,893
Iies the future happiness of my people,

481
00:57:28,979 --> 00:57:31,267
and the peace

482
00:57:31,356 --> 00:57:33,395
of this realm.

483
00:57:35,193 --> 00:57:39,605
Let that be upon your conscience also.

484
00:57:46,287 --> 00:57:48,991
My Lords, the House will divide.

485
00:57:58,215 --> 00:58:00,254
Walsingham... !

486
00:58:00,342 --> 00:58:04,837
I would know on what authority
you have kept us locked up here.

487
00:58:04,930 --> 00:58:08,879
Your Graces must forgive me,
but you are now free to go.

488
00:58:08,975 --> 00:58:13,517
I am sure this infernal work
has not saved your bastard Queen.

489
00:58:14,939 --> 00:58:17,690
Her Majesty... has won the argument.

490
00:58:18,734 --> 00:58:20,773
By what count ?

491
00:58:21,696 --> 00:58:24,269
By five, Your Grace.

492
00:58:25,950 --> 00:58:27,989
Five.

493
00:58:29,828 --> 00:58:32,116
You will be damned for this !

494
00:58:32,205 --> 00:58:36,332
And I pray God your wretched soul
will burn in hell !

495
00:59:17,165 --> 00:59:19,869
Report back to me at break of day.

496
01:00:04,835 --> 01:00:07,041
Enchante.

497
01:00:11,216 --> 01:00:12,081
No !

498
01:00:12,175 --> 01:00:15,674
Because... I am Anjou !

499
01:00:18,640 --> 01:00:21,510
Yes, I am Anjou, yes ! I am Anjou.

500
01:00:25,980 --> 01:00:28,186
My God ! She loves it !

501
01:00:35,739 --> 01:00:37,778
And I can't wait...

502
01:00:37,866 --> 01:00:42,611
I dream of the moment
when we are naked together in bed

503
01:00:42,704 --> 01:00:46,404
where I can stroke your thigh
and perhaps even

504
01:00:46,500 --> 01:00:48,575
your quinny ?

