01:00:49,836 --> 01:00:51,627
Would you like that ?

506
01:00:51,713 --> 01:00:53,871
Remove your hand.

507
01:00:53,965 --> 01:00:57,049
Perhaps, Your Grace,
we shall think on it, but...

508
01:00:57,135 --> 01:01:01,262
- I am deeply religious.
- But I am very religious, too.

509
01:01:01,347 --> 01:01:04,217
Very religious, yes !

510
01:01:09,688 --> 01:01:14,563
THE VATICAN

511
01:01:20,073 --> 01:01:24,200
Your Holiness,
the priest from England is here.

512
01:01:43,596 --> 01:01:49,265
